message.content: The paper does not mention any specific arXiv CS sub-category. However, based on the nature of the task and the use of sequence-to-sequence neural models, some likely arXiv CS sub-categories could be: cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
